race.comment: CAVILL TYCOON (3) makes the move from VIC to WA and his recent trial at lark hill was very impressive. The inside draw can see him close to the speed for Hearn and his ratings last start stack right up for a race of this quality. Looks well placed and can make a statement in his stable debut. I'M THAT GIRL (5) got the job done at this track and trip prior to the spell, scoring by 1.3L after being on the speed. Cooper's claim comes in handy and she has options from the barrier. No trial coming in is a niggle, but he can feature prominently if he's up to the mark. KAMIKAZE FIGHTER (4) drops back from the mile first-up today. Likely to get back from the draw but he comes into this without a recent trial. Can make his presence felt. ALOTOFBANTER (1) was placed first-up last campaign and if he runs up to that effort he can be in the finish. OUTLAW MUSIC (2) bolted in at the trials recently and looks ready to run a big race first-up.
